## рџљЂ Setup Instructions

### 1. Install dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

### 2. Setup MongoDB Atlas
- Go to https://cloud.mongodb.com
- Create free account в†’ New Project в†’ Free Cluster
- Database Access в†’ Add new user (username + password)
- Network Access в†’ Add IP в†’ 0.0.0.0/0 (allow all)
- Connect в†’ Drivers в†’ Copy connection string

### 3. Create .env file
```bash
cp .env.example .env
```
Fill in your values in `.env`:
- `MONGO_URI` вЂ” your MongoDB Atlas connection string
- `JWT_SECRET` вЂ” any long random string
- `ADMIN_EMAIL` вЂ” seemazala0422@gmail.com
- `ADMIN_PASSWORD` вЂ” your admin password
- `EMAIL_USER` вЂ” your Gmail
- `EMAIL_PASS` вЂ” Gmail App Password (not regular password)

### 4. Gmail App Password Setup
- Google Account в†’ Security в†’ 2-Step Verification (enable)
- App Passwords в†’ Select app: Mail в†’ Generate
- Copy the 16-character password в†’ paste in EMAIL_PASS

### 5. Seed the database (run once)
```bash
npm run seed
```
This creates:
- Admin account
- 4 initial projects

### 6. Start the server
```bash
# Development (auto-restart)
npm run dev

# Production
npm start
```

---

## рџ“Ў API Endpoints

### Auth
| Method | Route | Access | Description |
|--------|-------|--------|-------------|
| POST | /api/auth/login | Public | Admin login |
| GET | /api/auth/me | Private | Get profile |
| PUT | /api/auth/change-password | Private | Change password |

### Projects
| Method | Route | Access | Description |
|--------|-------|--------|-------------|
| GET | /api/projects | Public | Get active projects |
| GET | /api/projects/:id | Public | Get single project |
| GET | /api/projects/admin/all | Private | All projects (admin) |
| POST | /api/projects | Private | Create project |
| PUT | /api/projects/:id | Private | Update project |
| DELETE | /api/projects/:id | Private | Delete project |
| PATCH | /api/projects/:id/toggle | Private | Toggle active |

### Contact
| Method | Route | Access | Description |
|--------|-------|--------|-------------|
| POST | /api/contact | Public | Submit form |
| GET | /api/contact | Private | Get all messages |
| PATCH | /api/contact/:id/read | Private | Mark as read |
| PATCH | /api/contact/:id/replied | Private | Mark as replied |
| DELETE | /api/contact/:id | Private | Delete message |

---

## рџЊђ Deployment on Render (Free)

1. Push code to GitHub (don't commit .env!)
2. Go to https://render.com в†’ New Web Service
3. Connect GitHub repo
4. Settings:
   - Build Command: `npm install`
   - Start Command: `npm start`
5. Add Environment Variables (from your .env)
6. Deploy!

